{"tid":1478373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民陣上訴失敗：入嚟表達意見","createTime":"2019-08-16T13:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:24:12.000Z","uid":87915,"like":257,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"9da513451a40a461c841a5c28db44e99d5693884","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"預期失望的了<br />\n<br />\n我想表達一個意見：<br />\n1. 因為人多，民陣呼籲市民由中環或北角出，行「行人路」去維園集會<br />\n<br />\n2. 開始行唔到果陣，請直接坐低 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者直接天后 或 銅鑼灣出   慢慢坐到去金鐘 / 北角<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n事後行動，相信有其他post 討論<br />\n<br />\n要比和理非感受唔到 「原來我出嚟係有危險」嘅方案」"},{"pid":"a46b52e68b856b226e6754a57450902ad891ac5e","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ce27acbd1dfe4c669536b27cfd8bd8ad0fc8ea1e","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"8.18  坐爆港島"},{"pid":"6febf71d4ece8a0f95fc22cc3b04f5ab798589a1","tid":1478373,"uid":19055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"照去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b703864f45b147ec703045a4149a2e6c2ba244","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島"},{"pid":"26e39d859770827443646c5baedeb85a4fee9a6c","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:24:55.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fc5e46d7dc60d9302e5611ac5aebff394bea7a","tid":1478373,"uid":303422,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"[大腦]應對黑衫大陸鬼<br />\n唔係要全部check ，但係可以不定期check ，如暗號，之前有post 話有海關見大量黑衫大陸人嚟香港，係時候要拆招，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位大腦開啟</span></strong><br />\n本人先舉一例，暗號:入實驗室㩒緊急制<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"2504544605e5ab914cc0b03d494fc98ec169b2f7","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e55e91244af2a2b47cdf2c781004476269220d","tid":1478373,"uid":122985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"坐爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf26623c7ddf7581c60be09b83f79143da2b1b4","tid":1478373,"uid":258439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實大家可以由中環一齊行去維園集會<br />\n效果應該差唔多"},{"pid":"eb2b317cc51ee89115b722539e57f05a00d1b7b3","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島"},{"pid":"e06ea7238c4104e16a6a6ce2983776de90073001","tid":1478373,"uid":30150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cfac1016042ab11570c989083171b78594ebc0","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0306cc7634a91fb831bae6e3c946b244c9bf72","tid":1478373,"uid":21398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"示威又禁！暴力又話暴力！<br />\n我屌你老母呀！日日都出黎迫鳩香港人！<br />\n我就去撳哂D錢同轉MPF去北美基金！<br />\n禁撚埋我丫笨！"},{"pid":"964c36b062dcde69f4482c43a95253d960597a44","tid":1478373,"uid":153781,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"分析大家可以點應對818反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475432</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n入黎傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多巴絲對818有諗法！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n總括post入邊大家意見：<br />\n818不衝 不圍 不挑釁 不設防 能放能收 坐爆維園<br />\n<br />\n有手足提出：<br />\n<br />\n1.唔佔馬路 齋坐行人路（坐行人路唔係非法集會？有冇法律手足講下）<br />\n<br />\n2.記得戴定口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同頭盔或帽，保護自己<br />\n全世界帶眼罩<br />\n<br />\n3.如果有人行跡可疑 就示威者手鏈圍大圈 圈入面就記者同幾位勇d嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果冇野大家唔會驚 如果有野就制服佢 搵證據 俾記者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 維園冇位就坐係沿途商埸 一齊睇live 順便幫人哋罷市<br />\n<br />\n5. 避開坐爆之前同黑社會發生衝突嘅位置，避免引起衝突，恐慌<br />\n<br />\n6. 無論所有交通工具都金鐘落，行去維園，行唔到就坐<br />\n<br />\n7. 64當年有軍火隨街放，大家記住唔好拎同點！唔好俾藉囗中共鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n8. -出得嚟就要同自己打定最壞打算，無論咩人都係<br />\n-要克服你嘅恐慌 有突發事出現，<br />\n同隔離嗰個一齊分擔<br />\n-唔好因爲緊張亂講野，唔好因爲緊張亂信人<br />\n9.夠鐘就散場 下次再遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n試下說 勇武手法/和理非手法<br />\n任何手足都可以唔同場合，用唔同手法做事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e20074a1ce550c3cb609182b401ef272fcf292","tid":1478373,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"坐爆港島"},{"pid":"f1743f8fa3e1c46a90b064618a9f61710b286d9f","tid":1478373,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"818坐爆港島"},{"pid":"cbd724b138390e08c300b97391528b2f3e60332d","tid":1478373,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"唔好早上10點就開始！根本聚唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9752003cf8cf1b3b8d8b296e42186dfd98f1dc","tid":1478373,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"北角要小心 出得就要備戰 <br />\n唔係要早動打人 但唔係比人屠殺"},{"pid":"fff4b8301828914527895aeca020eeba2993b5a6","tid":1478373,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"係咪話班撐狗同一日係金鐘集會 咁我地個路線應該點"},{"pid":"8ab39618c806c4d45a7867f460a4872d609b6f21","tid":1478373,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Z4FHMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Z4FHMU.png&h=bb8bc822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zq0Q40o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZq0Q40o.png&h=51866ca6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb9d4b0e6e0d51a67f12123f717885691c5153bb","tid":1478373,"uid":287032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好由北角去！！！<br />\n應該集中一個方向<br />\n倒灌去中環金鐘！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8427bfbf8dcfee5697a1225c1a955a2436eddcde","tid":1478373,"uid":24036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，而家我地通知我地遊行，憑咩ject我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731cb1d2db8270285e58158d36d212f1c9483371","tid":1478373,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9d4b0e6e0d51a67f12123f717885691c5153bb","tid":1478373,"uid":287032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"<span styl